PN,35501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,FA mother who suffered three
OL,7,Fmiscarriages hopes sharing her story
OL,8,Fwill help other mothers in rural
OL,9,Fareas, as a new study has found
OL,10,Flocation determines access to post-
OL,11,Fbaby loss care.
OL,13,FRebecca King, from Castle Douglas, has
OL,14,Flost three babies, all in the second
OL,15,Ftrimester - the time when many mothers
OL,16,Ffeel safe enough to share the news of
OL,17,Ftheir pregnancy and prepare for their
OL,18,Fchild.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,FRebecca says that after each of the
OL,7,Fmiscarriages she was left confused and
OL,8,Funaware of where to get specialised
OL,9,Fhelp.
OL,11,FShe told ITV Border: "I wasn't sure
OL,12,Fwhat to do. I had this empty, empty
OL,13,Ffeeling that we didn't get that baby
OL,14,Fthat we wanted so much. It was all I
OL,15,Fcould think about, it was all
OL,16,Fconsuming.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"It doesn't happen more than once, you
OL,7,Fdon't hear about it. I remember at
OL,8,Fthat stage feeling really alone with
OL,9,Fmy grief, because it felt so surreal
OL,10,Fthat this had happened twice in a row
OL,11,Fwithout reason."
OL,13,FResearch from the University of
OL,14,FAberdeen and baby loss charity Tommy's
OL,15,Fhas now shown women who suffer the
OL,16,Floss of a baby during the second
OL,17,Ftrimester are more likely to
OL,18,Fexperience a further miscarriage in
OL,19,Ffuture pregnancies.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,FIt also found that where mothers live
OL,7,Fdetermines access to and the quality
OL,8,Fof specialist care.
OL,10,FJust 45% of respondents to the survey
OL,11,Freported that follow-up appointments
OL,12,Ftook place in a dedicated pregnancy
OL,13,Floss clinic after a miscarriage.
OL,15,FRebecca said: "Sometimes living in a
OL,16,Frural area can be fantastic - I've had
OL,17,Fthe same midwives throughout the whole
OL,18,Fpregnancy. It meant the aftercare when
OL,19,FI lost the little ones was great,
OL,20,Fbecause they knew me.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"At the same time, we don't have a
OL,7,Fspecialised maternity unit. It's just
OL,8,Fknowing where to signpost these women
OL,9,Fto, so they're not having to fight for
OL,10,Ftheir care."
OL,12,FSupport and advice for those going
OL,13,Fthrough baby loss can be found here:
OL,15,FThe Mariposa Trust
OL,17,FThe Lullaby Trust
OL,19,FAbout Saying Goodbye
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,FProfessor Alex Heazell, the director
OL,7,Fof Tommy's Maternal and Fetal Health
OL,8,FResearch Centre, said: "There was
OL,9,Freally big variation from very, very
OL,10,Fgood to care you think would not give
OL,11,Fwomen good experiences.
OL,13,F"We want to understand this better, so
OL,14,Fwe can hopefully have some
OL,15,Fstandardisation of practice and bring
OL,16,Fall of the care up to a better quality
OL,17,Ffor all women."
OL,19,FRebecca hopes sharing her story will
OL,20,Fprevent other mothers from facing a
OL,21,Fsimilar fate.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"I have six children, but I only have
OL,7,Fthree with me. To use their story to
OL,8,Fhelp others has always been my focus.
OL,9,FWe can't change what happened to me,
OL,10,Fbut I can think about my babies
OL,11,Fhelping other babies in the future."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,FIn response, NHS Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fsaid: "NHS Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,Frecognises the distress experienced by
OL,9,Fanyone who goes through the loss of a
OL,10,Fbaby in the second trimester. It
OL,11,Fappreciates how devastating this can
OL,12,Fbe for families and is committed to
OL,13,Fproviding compassionate care, clear
OL,14,Finformation, and specialist support
OL,15,Fthroughout their journey.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"Second trimester losses can occur for
OL,7,Fa number of reasons. However, even
OL,8,Fwith thorough investigation it is not
OL,9,Falways possible to identify a clear
OL,10,Fcause, which we understand can be
OL,11,Fextremely difficult for families.
OL,13,F"To ensure high quality care, we
OL,14,Ffollow national evidence based
OL,15,Fguidance, including the Royal College
OL,16,Fof Obstetricians and Gynaecologists'
OL,17,Frecommendations for recurrent
OL,18,Fmiscarriage and NICE guidance relating
OL,19,Fto cervical incompetence and the
OL,20,Fprevention of preterm birth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"Care is tailored to individual
OL,7,Fcircumstances and may include a range
OL,8,Fof investigations following a
OL,9,Fsecondtrimester loss. Immediate
OL,10,Finvestigations can involve maternal
OL,11,Fassessment, examination of the baby,
OL,12,Fpostmortem where
OL,14,Fappropriate, placenta pathology and
OL,15,Fgenetic testing, all of which can help
OL,16,Fdetermine whether a cause can be
OL,17,Fidentified.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"NHS Dumfries and Galloway also
OL,7,Fprovides a specialist Consultantled
OL,8,FRecurrent Miscarriage Clinic. This
OL,9,Fallows for further investigations that
OL,10,Fcan only be performed outside of
OL,11,Fpregnancy or require time to pass
OL,12,Fafter a loss, such as
OL,14,Fthrombophilia screening, uterine
OL,15,Fscanning and other relevant
OL,16,Fassessments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"Alongside clinical care, emotional
OL,7,Fand practical support is a vital part
OL,8,Fof what we provide. We offer
OL,9,Fbereavement support and information on
OL,10,Fburial options, and we signpost
OL,11,Ffamilies to organisations such as
OL,12,FSANDS and the Sophie Catherine Mills
OL,13,FCharity, which offer specialist
OL,14,Fsupport at this extremely difficult
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1772723489
OL,3,CMum who suffered three miscarriages
OL,4,Cwants better post-baby loss care
OL,6,F"We are committed to listening and
OL,7,Flearning from every experience. In
OL,8,Faddition, NHS Dumfries and Galloway is
OL,9,Factively implementing the Scottish
OL,10,FGovernment's Miscarriage Framework,
OL,11,Fwhich sets out national expectations
OL,12,Ffor
OL,14,Fimproving care, support and followup
OL,15,Ffor anyone experiencing miscarriage."
OL,17,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,18,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,19,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,20,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/13
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
